.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda
There are 2 different nationalities: mexican, egyptian
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, montecristo
2 different pets are kept: dog, lizard
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, volleyball
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
2. the oliveros-smoker is the mexican##1
3. the oliveros-smoker is in an even position##4
4. the egyptian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | almond-milk |
| Nationality           | egyptian  | mexican     |
| Cigar   | montecristo       | oliveros      |
| Pet           | dog        | lizard      |
| Sport         | volleyball | surfing     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, sudoku
The people have 2 different jobs:  doctor, dressmaker
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, mexican
There are 2 different favourite colors: lilac, red
House: craftsman, cottage
1. the mexican is on the left or right of the person who likes red##3
2. the craftsman house is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an odd position##4
4. the dressmaker is the cottage house##1
5. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby         | sudoku     | puzzles    |
| Job           | doctor     | dressmaker |
| Nationality   | mexican    | japanese   |
| Color         | lilac | red   |
| House     | craftsman | cottage |

