.:: Puzzle 5x2-Level-4-4::.
There 2 different types of food: cranberry, kiwi
City: prague, boston
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: blues, pop
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, nigerian
There are 2 different favourite colors: red, green
1. the fan of blues is on the right of the person who likes red##1
2. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
3. the nigerian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |
| Food          | kiwi     | cranberry     |
| City   | prague   | boston        |
| Music-Genre   | pop      | blues         |
| Nationality   | nigerian | italian       |
| Color         | red  | green |

